<hw>colors</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a flag flown by a ship to
show its nationality.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ensign, colours.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a distinguishing emblem; <as>as, his tie proclaimed
